_header: Undo your gates princes to me
_description: Dialogue between Christ and the Princes of Hell — seven lines in a Latin sermon for Good Friday modelled on Ps. 24:7-10

BodLatTheD1.First Lines:
On do ȝour ȝatys princys to mehelle ȝatis oppen
                    ȝe…
BodLatTheD1.Last Lines:
…I am lord of strength & myhteAnd a stalworthi lord in ich
                    a syȝth
